reviewText: This is worth it, if you want to improve your fishing game. Very happy.
Pretty good info and underwater footage. It has some top notch presenters.  I like the pictures and info on shaky head worming.

These guys are the pros (literally) in bass fishing. Every show has something to offer and if you want to improve your skills in bass fishing and like to get that info from videos, don't overlook this or any of the Bass Pro show videos.
